E-08 LARGE KANBAN KIND  IS DIFFERENT FROM CONTENTS OF M/F.
E-09 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT  M/F EXIST.
E-10 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DON'T EXIST.
